Requirement:
[Student]
- Viewable lecture slides 
- Submitting homework 
- Be able to give tutor feedback 
- Allow consultation meetings 
- Able to message tutors or lecturers 
- Able to write a direct response under assignment in application



[Lecturer]
- Be able to post lecture slides and tutorials 
- Check attendances using the school WIFI
- Show the total percentage of attendances

[Wont have for lecturer]
- Allow lecturers to grant themselves higher system permission
- Allow lecturers to change student's grade after they are finalised
- Allow lecturers to modify student's tutor feedback
- Allow lecturers to edit student's information
- Allow lecturers to delete students from the system
- Allow lecturers to view private messages between students
- Allow lecturers to disable nofication systems for students
- Allow lecturers to change system security and login methods
- Allow lecturers to create new roles permissions
- Allow lecturers to change system language and global application settings







